            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1871_09_14_Kniffler_Nagasaki_von_William_Younger_Co_Edinburgh_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>
            <hi rend="print">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01132">ABBEY &amp; HOLYROOD BREWERIES</orgName>
               <lb/>
               <figure>
                  <figDesc>Firmenlogo von Younger &amp; Co. eine Fahne mit dem Firmennamen WILLIAM YOUNGER &amp; Co. unterhalb der Fahne ESTABLISHED 1749</figDesc>
               </figure>
               <placeName ref="K00598">Edinburgh</placeName>
            </hi>
            <date when="1871-09-14">14 Sept <hi rend="print">187</hi> 1</date>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="left">Messrs <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler &amp;Co</orgName>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="K00514">Nagasaki</placeName>
               <lb/> Dear Sirs</seg>
            <lb/> We dated our last<lb/>
            <unclear reason="illegible">respects</unclear>
            <date when="1871-07-06">6 July</date> + now reply to your<lb/> favor p <date when="1871-07-14">14<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> same</date>
            <choice>
               <abbr>A/C </abbr>
               <expan>account</expan>
            </choice>Sales<lb/> ex <name type="ship" ref="K01818">Chanticleer</name> our
               <unclear>friend</unclear>
            <lb/> exception to your<lb/> guarantee <unclear>cant</unclear> which is a very<lb/>
            unusual change especially with<lb/> such adverse results. Your friends<lb/> at
               <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName> have <term type="commercial" ref="K01523">remittet</term> us<lb/>
            <term type="commercial" ref="K01522">£</term>
            <measure type="currency" quantity="53.10" unit="britPound">53.10</measure>
            <unclear>/</unclear> Bill a 4/5½ = <term type="commercial" ref="K01508">$</term>
            <measure type="currency" quantity="240" unit="mex$">240-</measure>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="right">Yours faithfully<lb/>
               <unclear>p</unclear>
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01132">W<hi rend="superscript">m</hi>. <hi rend="underline">Younger</hi> &amp; C.</orgName>
            </seg>
         </p>
